definitions.definition: A village in Stillington and Whitton parish, Stockton-on-Tees borough , County Durham , England ( OS grid ref NZ3723 ) .
A village and civil parish in North Yorkshire , England , previously in Hambleton district ( OS grid ref SE5867 ) .
